Criterion_Table_1.label: Criterion Table
Criterion_Table_1.query:
mea = load "${App.Datasets.CriterionWithMeasure_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";
mea = foreach mea generate
coalesce('Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
coalesce('Criterion.Name', "-") as 'Criterion.Name', 
coalesce('Criterion.txl_Content__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
coalesce('Criterion.txl_Description__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
coalesce('Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', "-") as 'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
coalesce('Criterion.txl_Statement__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
coalesce('Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c', "-") as 'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
coalesce('Measure.Name', "-") as 'Measure.Name',
coalesce('Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c', "-") as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
coalesce('Measure.AssignedTo.Name', "-") as 'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
coalesce(substr('Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c', 1, 10), "-") as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c';
mea = group mea by (
'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
'Criterion.Name', 
'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
'Measure.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c');

mea = foreach mea generate 
'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c' as 'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
'Criterion.Name' as 'Criterion.Name', 
'Criterion.txl_Content__c' as 'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Description__c' as 'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c' as 'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Statement__c' as 'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c' as 'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
'Measure.Name'as 'Measure.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c' as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
'Measure.AssignedTo.Name' as 'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c' as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c',
count() as 'count';

cri = load "${App.Datasets.PACCRM_PACC_Freeze_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";
cri = foreach cri generate 
coalesce('txt_Numbering__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
coalesce('Name', "-") as 'Criterion.Name', 
coalesce('txl_Content__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
coalesce('txl_Description__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
coalesce('pkl_Relevance__c', "-") as 'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
coalesce('txl_Statement__c', "-") as 'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
coalesce('UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c', "-") as 'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
"-â €" as 'Measure.Name',
"-" as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
"-" as 'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
"-" as 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c',
count() as 'count';

final = union mea, cri;
final = group final by (
'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
'Criterion.Name', 
'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
'Measure.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c');
final = foreach final generate
'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
'Criterion.Name', 
'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
'Measure.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c',
sum('count')/sum(sum('count')) over ([..] partition by 'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c') as 'No of Measures';
final = filter final by ('No of Measures' == 1 && 'Measure.Name' == "-â €") || 'Measure.Name' == "-" || 'Measure.Name' != "-â €";
final = foreach final generate
'Criterion.txt_Numbering__c', 
'Criterion.Name', 
'Criterion.txl_Content__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Description__c', 
'Criterion.pkl_Relevance__c', 
'Criterion.txl_Statement__c',
'Criterion.UP2GO_2T__pkl_Rating__c',
'Measure.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__txa_Description__c',
'Measure.AssignedTo.Name',
'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c';
final = order final by ('Criterion.txt_Numbering__c' desc, 'Measure.UP2GO_2T__dat_DueDate__c' asc);
